The ideal profile will:
-  Identify new market trends, business opportunities and manage key industry relationships;
-  Build a case and recommendations for how to set up our in-market operations in certain countries across Latin America;
-  Provide clear direction to our business executives, product marketing teams and engineers, to prioritize market opportunities across Latin America;
-  Advise on all aspects of market intelligence including engagement with Tax, Legal, Commercial and Government Affairs;
-  Deliver excellent reporting to all stakeholders across the organization;
-  Be a passionate advocate for Apple and its products with a strong attention to detail, showing high energy and a positive attitude.

Description
• We advise on business transformation solutions with our partners in the Industry for Apple’s Enterprise Major Accounts in the Public Sector.
• We develop account plans aligned with our customers’ strategies, assess their progress and guide them on the journey of transformation to mobility, while growing and expanding adoption of the Apple ecosystem.
• We effectively execute on plans by cross-functionally connecting with Inside Sales, Systems Engineers, reseller and strategic partners, and then we create demand generation activities, identify new opportunities, accurately forecast,and coordinate fulfillment logistics.
Role Objectives 
• You will demonstrate and develop strong network within government, public sector, system integrators and local blue chips to generate leads;
• You will design, sell and lead large-scale projects involving Apple products and services;
• You will lead cross-functional teams to ensure timely delivery of the projects;
